no one has ever survived what you're

01:13:53.783 --> 01:13:54.545
asking me to do,

01:13:55.085 --> 01:13:57.564
which is to expose and condemn Muhammad

01:13:57.765 --> 01:14:00.105
and Allah and the Quran.

01:14:00.126 --> 01:14:00.886
Well, I mean,

01:14:00.926 --> 01:14:03.246
let's just pretend now that you are who

01:14:03.265 --> 01:14:03.886
you say you are.

01:14:05.806 --> 01:14:06.686
Can I negotiate?

01:14:06.726 --> 01:14:07.506
Because, well,

01:14:07.587 --> 01:14:08.927
it seems like a death sentence.

01:14:09.887 --> 01:14:10.007
Now,

01:14:10.028 --> 01:14:11.188
I'm not so sure that sounds like a

01:14:11.228 --> 01:14:13.028
lot of fun.

01:14:13.087 --> 01:14:13.628
I said, sure.

01:14:14.088 --> 01:14:15.469
What do you want, kid?

01:14:17.273 --> 01:14:18.252
I laid out three things.

01:14:18.273 --> 01:14:19.293
These are the three things I want.

01:14:20.354 --> 01:14:22.114
He said, okay, that sounds fine with me.

01:14:22.154 --> 01:14:22.914
Reach into your pocket.

01:14:23.836 --> 01:14:24.115
I did.

01:14:24.975 --> 01:14:27.337
There was the answer to the three things

01:14:27.417 --> 01:14:27.756
I wanted.

01:14:28.318 --> 01:14:28.818
I said, okay,

01:14:28.837 --> 01:14:29.978
so now you've got my attention.

01:14:31.139 --> 01:14:31.998
I guess we're going to begin.

01:14:33.020 --> 01:14:35.201
I guess I'm going to find out.

01:14:35.740 --> 01:14:38.841
And here we are.

01:14:38.881 --> 01:14:40.222
Ten thousand death threats later.

01:14:40.983 --> 01:14:41.962
Thirty-five books.

01:14:42.042 --> 01:14:43.524
A hundred thousand hours later.

01:14:45.011 --> 01:14:45.591
thousands,

01:14:45.631 --> 01:14:48.373
tens of thousands of hours of radio and

01:14:48.434 --> 01:14:49.533
now of vlogs.

01:14:50.475 --> 01:14:50.996
And here we are,

01:14:51.916 --> 01:14:54.478
telling you the story of God,

01:14:54.818 --> 01:14:58.280
revealing His message as completely and as

01:14:58.400 --> 01:15:00.582
accurately as has ever been presented

01:15:00.643 --> 01:15:01.082
before.

01:15:02.823 --> 01:15:04.546
And I can tell you that two years

01:15:04.605 --> 01:15:07.247
into that, I had learned enough.

01:15:08.188 --> 01:15:10.029
that one of my closest friends at the

01:15:10.069 --> 01:15:10.248
time,

01:15:10.309 --> 01:15:11.789
and I was one of his closest friends,

01:15:11.829 --> 01:15:14.211
was Dr. Jerry Falwell,

01:15:14.832 --> 01:15:16.672
the Reverend who had been on the cover

01:15:16.813 --> 01:15:18.434
multiple times of Time Magazine.

01:15:18.474 --> 01:15:20.054
He was the head of the Moral Majority.

01:15:21.454 --> 01:15:23.815
He was the first televangelist.

01:15:24.877 --> 01:15:26.717
Remarkable man, actually a very lovable,

01:15:26.818 --> 01:15:28.939
likable man in person,

01:15:28.958 --> 01:15:30.140
a great conversationalist,

01:15:30.180 --> 01:15:32.520
exceedingly kind to people in his inner

01:15:32.581 --> 01:15:32.940
circle.

01:15:33.561 --> 01:15:35.082
And we spent a lot of time together.

01:15:35.103 --> 01:15:35.243
I mean,

01:15:35.643 --> 01:15:37.583
thousands and thousands of hours together.

01:15:38.882 --> 01:15:40.502
And very early on,

01:15:40.523 --> 01:15:43.024
and it was before Yahowah had called me

01:15:43.043 --> 01:15:43.863
to ask me to do this,

01:15:43.884 --> 01:15:45.185
that I'd built my relationship with him.

01:15:45.284 --> 01:15:47.966
And as I was getting to know Yahowah,

01:15:48.206 --> 01:15:50.286
and I had already abandoned Christianity

01:15:50.326 --> 01:15:50.886
by that time,

01:15:52.806 --> 01:15:54.167
it became obvious that everything in

01:15:54.186 --> 01:15:55.167
Christianity was a lie.

01:15:55.948 --> 01:15:57.887
And so I asked for a meeting with

01:15:58.047 --> 01:16:00.288
Jerry Falwell, the pastor's pastor,

01:16:00.309 --> 01:16:00.748
if you will.

01:16:01.488 --> 01:16:02.630
And I said, I want you to bring,

01:16:02.649 --> 01:16:03.090
please,

01:16:03.170 --> 01:16:07.511
the head of the Hebrew church

01:16:08.699 --> 01:16:09.480
division of your,

01:16:09.881 --> 01:16:11.622
he owned Liberty University.

01:16:12.042 --> 01:16:13.585
So bring your top Hebrew scholar.

01:16:14.145 --> 01:16:18.128
I want you to bring your top theologians.

01:16:18.628 --> 01:16:18.828
Really,

01:16:18.849 --> 01:16:20.690
I've got a whole series of things I

01:16:20.711 --> 01:16:22.573
want to go through and I want them

01:16:22.613 --> 01:16:23.753
to be able to challenge what I have

01:16:23.793 --> 01:16:24.675
to say.

01:16:25.175 --> 01:16:26.296
And I went through all the reasons that

01:16:26.315 --> 01:16:28.557
Christianity was false that I'd already

01:16:29.057 --> 01:16:29.498
deduced.

01:16:29.578 --> 01:16:31.621
And that's not even a fraction of one

01:16:31.661 --> 01:16:34.082
percent of what I know now.

01:16:34.203 --> 01:16:34.923
At the end of all that,

01:16:35.871 --> 01:16:38.091
Not a single time did any one of

01:16:38.112 --> 01:16:40.551
the Hebrew scholars challenge anything I

01:16:40.591 --> 01:16:40.792
said.

01:16:41.811 --> 01:16:42.972
And Jerry just looked at me,

01:16:43.052 --> 01:16:44.512
put his hand on the top of my

01:16:44.552 --> 01:16:45.332
hand, and he said,

01:16:46.974 --> 01:16:48.173
everything you've said is true.

01:16:49.953 --> 01:16:51.314
But if I were to say those things,

01:16:52.295 --> 01:16:54.315
the people that sit in the pews of

01:16:54.376 --> 01:16:57.235
my church and make donations wouldn't

01:16:57.275 --> 01:16:57.536
come.

01:16:58.556 --> 01:17:00.377
All of the envelopes that arrive daily

01:17:00.436 --> 01:17:03.457
here supporting my university wouldn't

01:17:03.497 --> 01:17:03.898
arrive.

01:17:05.069 --> 01:17:06.371
And if you say those things,

01:17:06.610 --> 01:17:09.935
they're going to label you a kook.

01:17:09.975 --> 01:17:12.958
So you want to go ask your pastor.

01:17:12.998 --> 01:17:14.381
Don't be surprised if he tells you the

01:17:14.400 --> 01:17:16.283
truth.

01:17:16.302 --> 01:17:19.306
They know it's a lie.

01:17:19.346 --> 01:17:20.087
Thank you for listening.